<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180525/020661.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/135/164/2277/148103880.jpg" alt="道服与汉服到底是不是一回事儿？"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/minsudaoyi2015/wenyi2015/list2015114162324.htm">文艺</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180525/020661.htm">道服与汉服到底是不是一回事儿？</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">汉服与道教道服一体同源，同是华夏文化之瑰宝，但二者之间仍旧有所差异。盖因汉服常因时代变化而移风易俗，而道教则始终保持传统。本文细数了当下惯用的道服类型，</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">万法勇</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%81%93%E6%9C%8D" title="道服">道服</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%B1%89%E6%9C%8D" title="汉服">汉服</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%96%8B%E9%86%AE%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%AA" title="斋醮科仪">斋醮科仪</a></li>
</ul>
<a target="_blank" class="comments" href="/a/20180525/020661.htm">16</a>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180524/030774.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/192/133/2277/148096032.jpg" alt="仙人骑凤披彩霞：武当山金殿屋脊兽的独特魅力"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/minsudaoyi2015/jianzhu2015/list2015114161721.htm">建筑</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180524/030774.htm">仙人骑凤披彩霞：武当山金殿屋脊兽的独特魅</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">武当山道教建筑群，是道教建筑中的瑰宝，独具特色。本文从武当山太和宫金殿的屋脊兽入手，将之与当时的建筑脊兽进行对比。重点突出了“骑凤仙人”形象，并对其加以</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">止水</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E6%AD%A6%E5%BD%93%E5%B1%B1" title="武当山">武当山</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%B1%8B%E8%84%8A%E5%85%BD" title="屋脊兽">屋脊兽</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%A4%AA%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%AB" title="太和宫">太和宫</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%87%91%E6%AE%BF" title="金殿">金殿</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
<li><div class="q_tpwrap clearfix">
<a target="_blank" class="pic" href="/a/20180517/019588.htm"><img src="http://img1.gtimg.com/rushidao/pics/hv1/46/93/2276/148020661.jpg" alt="为何道教很难产生“灭霸”？"></a><div class="text">
<div class="name">
<a target="_blank" class="navigation" href="http://rufodao.qq.com/l/daoxue/minsudaoyi2015/wenyi2015/list2015114162324.htm">文艺</a><a target="_blank" class="t" href="/a/20180517/019588.htm">为何道教很难产生“灭霸”？</a>
</div>
<div class="desp">近日《复联3》上映，大反派灭霸为了他认为的“正义”毁灭了世界上一半的物种。笔者认为这一行为与道教不合，因为道教以道为立教根基，主张道法自然，不应以人的局</div>
<div class="tips">
<span class="name">三晚居士</span><ul class="clearfix">
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E9%81%93" title="道">道</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1" title="电影">电影</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://rushidao.qq.com/dc_column_article/TagsList.htm?tags=%E5%A4%8D%E8%81%943" title="复联3">复联3</a></li>
</ul>
<a target="_blank" class="comments" href="/a/20180517/019588.htm">62</a>
</div>
</div>
</div></li>
</ul>
